      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Invoice extraction (upgraded)\n\n**Before activating, you must:**\n1. Re-select all credentials marked `REPLACE_ME` (Gmail, Google Sheets, Slack) — imported JSON cannot carry your credential IDs across accounts.\n2. Pick your real spreadsheet + tab in **both** Google Sheets nodes.\n3. Pick your real Slack channel in the two Slack sendAndWait nodes.\n4. Pick or create a Gmail label in **Label & Archive** (e.g. \"Invoices/Processed\").\n5. In n8n workflow Settings, set **Error Workflow** to this same workflow so the error branch fires.\n\n**Verify before trusting validation:** run one real invoice through and check the actual field names cradl returns under `body.output` — the Validate & Score node currently assumes invoice_number, vendor_name, currency, invoice_total, invoice_lines[].amount.",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 620,
        "color": 4
      }
    },
